  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the <span class=\"italic \">xy</span>-plane, the points <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"with coordinates negative 2 comma 3 \"></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"4 comma negative 5 \"></span></span> lie on the graph of which of the following linear functions?</p>\n",
